Survival Island
Survival Island
("the Game") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data when you use our Game.
1. Information We Do Not Collect
Personal Information:
The Game does not collect or store any personal information, such as your name, email address, phone number, or physical address.
Login Information:
There is no requirement to create an account or log in to use the Game.
Payment Information:
The Game does not offer in-app purchases or transactions, so no payment information is collected.
2. Information We May Collect
To enhance your experience, the Game may collect limited, non-personally identifiable data, such as:
Device Information:
Basic information about your device, such as the operating system version and device type, for performance optimization.
Game Performance Data:
Data related to game crashes, bugs, or errors to help us improve the Game’s functionality.
3. How We Use Collected Data
Any non-personal data collected is used solely to:
Improve the Game’s performance and user experience.
Identify and fix technical issues or bugs.
Ensure compatibility with different devices and operating systems.
4. Sharing of Information
We do not share, sell, or disclose your information to third parties, except as required by law or to protect the integrity of the Game (e.g., addressing security threats).
5. No Third-Party Ads
The Game does not display advertisements or use third-party advertising services.
6. Data Security
We prioritize the security of your information. Any data collected is handled with industry-standard security measures to prevent unauthorized access or misuse. However, no system can be completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
7. Children’s Privacy
The Game is designed for users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us at
premiumqualityapps.com@gmail.com
